Fight to the end!

800
01:12:33,240 --> 01:12:34,275
Fellow students!

801
01:12:34,680 --> 01:12:38,229
T'an Ssu-t'ung said
"successful reforms come with bloodshed",

802
01:12:38,520 --> 01:12:42,559
So let bloodshed and sacrifice begin with us!

803
01:12:42,720 --> 01:12:48,750
Charge!

804
01:12:51,560 --> 01:12:58,955
Come out!

805
01:13:02,400 --> 01:13:03,355
Young lady!

806
01:13:03,800 --> 01:13:05,791
Take your grievances to the prosecutors!

807
01:13:06,400 --> 01:13:08,356
You've come to the wrong place!

808
01:13:09,560 --> 01:13:14,076
My grievances are beyond the prosecutors!

809
01:13:14,600 --> 01:13:15,794
What do you mean?

810
01:13:18,200 --> 01:13:22,671
I'm pleading for 400 million Chinese.

811
01:13:22,840 --> 01:13:29,712
Come out!

812
